name: Recon
description:
This morning, the enemy in the area of Golay Pristan, Kherson region, attempted to land their DRGs on our shore.

The Armed Forces of Ukraine involved as many as four boats, the total number of enemy personnel was at least forty people.

One of the boats was supposed to distract us while the other three were landing.

As a result, only the distracting boat managed to land, but not on the shore, but on the bottom of the Dnieper.

The other three raced off home to lick their wounds

name: Russian Ural with ZU-23-2 Twerk to Death.
Ukrainian Drones Shot down
description: During this night and morning, 9 UAVs were recorded over the territory of the Republic of Crimea: 6 devices were shot down by air defense forces, 3 were jammed and landed by electronic warfare. One drone detonated in the Krasnogvardeisky district, the village of Dokuchaevo. There were no casualties, windows were broken in a number of houses. All services have left. Please remain calm and trust only trusted sources of information.
